title: Bug 121687 Exception throws when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell
description: When trying to export data from a table inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
OB: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from a table inside a grid cell.
EB: The data from the table inside the grid cell should be exported successfully.
SR:
1. Insert a grid.
2. Export data from the table inside the grid cell.
3. Ensure that the data is exported without any exceptions being thrown.
